<p><span style="white-space:nowrap"><a href="/w/index.php?title=Taxation_in_Antigua_and_Barbuda&amp;action=edit&amp;redlink=1" class="new" title="Taxation in Antigua and Barbuda (page does not exist)">Antigua and Barbuda</a>&#160;<b>·</b></span> <span style="white-space:nowrap"><a href="/w/index.php?title=Taxation_in_the_Bahamas&amp;action=edit&amp;redlink=1" class="new" title="Taxation in the Bahamas (page does not exist)">Bahamas</a>&#160;<b>·</b></span> <span style="white-space:nowrap"><a href="/w/index.php?title=Taxation_in_Barbados&amp;action=edit&amp;redlink=1" class="new" title="Taxation in Barbados (page does not exist)">Barbados</a>&#160;<b>·</b></span> <span style="white-space:nowrap"><a href="/w/index.php?title=Taxation_in_Belize&amp;action=edit&amp;redlink=1" class="new" title="Taxation in Belize (page does not exist)">Belize</a>&#160;<b>·</b></span> <span style="white-space:nowrap"><strong class="selflink">Canada</strong>&#160;<b>·</b></span> <span style="white-space:nowrap"><a href="/w/index.php?title=Taxation_in_Costa_Rica&amp;action=edit&amp;redlink=1" class="new" title="Taxation in Costa Rica (page does not exist)">Costa Rica</a>&#160;<b>·</b></span> <span style="white-space:nowrap"><a href="/w/index.php?title=Taxation_in_Cuba&amp;action=edit&amp;redlink=1" class="new" title="Taxation in Cuba (page does not exist)">Cuba</a>&#160;<b>·</b></span> <span style="white-space:nowrap"><a href="/w/index.php?title=Taxation_in_Dominica&amp;action=edit&amp;redlink=1" class="new" title="Taxation in Dominica (page does not exist)">Dominica</a>&#160;<b>·</b></span> <span style="white-space:nowrap"><a href="/w/index.php?title=Taxation_in_the_Dominican_Republic&amp;action=edit&amp;redlink=1" class="new" title="Taxation in the Dominican Republic (page does not exist)">Dominican Republic</a>&#160;<b>·</b></span> <span style="white-space:nowrap"><a href="/w/index.php?title=Taxation_in_El_Salvador&amp;action=edit&amp;redlink=1" class="new" title="Taxation in El Salvador